-07-03T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"搵人嘈交鬥屌就得   當年都係咁學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"極速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb070a2d4215b3cc04b4ca93142a61043803ad84","tid":727967,"uid":65854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"打 online game<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">當年就係係巨商學翻來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"52dbac7b1ec9cb03cc9151dab4f4bbcb3f13ed85","tid":727967,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"而家蝗中學 連速成都失傳？"},{"pid":"b89da9a37d864628f3202d601d88972007212fee","tid":727967,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52dbac7b1ec9cb03cc9151dab4f4bbcb3f13ed85","tid":727967,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"而家蝗中學 連速成都失傳？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"好似直接打蝗語拼音字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e6b3078cb18bcafd1418cbcb11e0e2d9089ced","tid":727967,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"d後生用普通話拼音<br />\n你參考下囉<br />\n反正班「中國香港人」係社會未來棟樑<br />\n遲早要跟佢地食飯"},{"pid":"ed73216307d172fbb6a4497edafeb3e477aa2e79","tid":727967,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"練練練練練練"},{"pid":"b28fffa67432686baa3887af8c85a3ea42ca6f52","tid":727967,"uid":163130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"多數公司都冇乜要求速成定倉頡，最緊要快同準啫，不過最好當然學倉頡啦。<br />\n<br />\n想盡快學識，第一步先買本倉頡書(個人覺得睇書比上網搵比較入腦)，起碼明白咗拆碼個原理先，再慢慢練習打 d 簡單字。熟少少之後就強迫自己堅持要用倉頡打(唔好再轉用筆劃或者拼音)，遇到唔識既字就睇返本書點拆，久而久之就會越打越快。<br />\n<br />\nPS 當年我自己練習時就係打自己鐘意既歌既歌詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8da3aee9d2ff0fe7dae70952ea5374c9c8d90c3","tid":727967,"uid":60321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"1.最緊要用岩工具 咁就易學好多<br />\n<br />\n- 買本倉頡書或者字典, 記下d口訣同個字母表, 我當時係google play買《24小時倉頡速學天書》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/183858_c1564a0486bcdeb9af453bae002d01a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F183858_c1564a0486bcdeb9af453bae002d01a2.png&h=42d6cdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 有d工具會逐part教你點拆, 會用顏色區分每個碼代表邊part<br />\n例如五色學倉頡或者依個網：<a href=\"http://input.foruto.com/cccls/cjzd.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finput.foruto.com%2Fcccls%2Fcjzd.html&d=D%2Bnk8INDadi3XGijexsOJMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e3208d5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://input.foruto.com/cccls/cjzd.html</a><br />\n如果開個網變左亂碼, 自己去google《Follow Me倉頡字典》線上查詢版<br />\n一唔識就查, 睇得多起碼明個邏輯, 唔洗純死記<br />\n<br />\n2. 逼自己用多d, 係電話刪哂其他輸入法, 只用倉頡<br />\n同埋電話d倉頡唔洗打到捉, 多數打頭一兩個碼知自己有無打錯, 初學會舒服d<br />\n<br />\n我用左九方十幾年, 上年轉 <br />\n第一日用黎背口訣同碼表, 跟住日日去玩ios個五色學倉頡個遊戲練習<br />\n一星期就識打, 無特別對文章練習, 最緊要用岩工具"},{"pid":"e142cedab9136cbca28423de98c78fa7d062fb59","tid":727967,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"見人用語音轉換"},{"pid":"02853d77b14a36aca050ea99836248507044046f","tid":727967,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"短時間有難度，但買本倉頡書學咗先，之後狂練，你識唔識打英文先，見好多人仲要望keyboard 話要學打倉頡"}]}